{"componentChunkName":"component---src-components-post-container-index-tsx","path":"/post/gatsby/gatsby-static-image/","result":{"data":{"allMarkdownRemark":{"edges":[{"node":{"html":"<p>포스트 목록에 썸네일 이미지를 추가하고 싶어서 <code class=\"language-text\">gatsby-plugin-image</code> 라이브러리의 <code class=\"language-text\">StaticImage</code>로 구현해 보고 있었다. 그런데 emotion의 <code class=\"language-text\">styled</code>를 적용하면 이미지가 아예 뜨질 않았다 😳</p>\n<p>또 프로필 이미지에는 <code class=\"language-text\">GatsbyImage</code>를 사용했는데, PC 화면에서는 스타일이 잘 적용되어 보이지만 모바일 화면에서는 적용되지 않은 채 보이는 일이 발생했다…</p>\n<h1>1. &#x3C;StaticImage/>에 스타일 적용하기</h1>\n<p><strong>emotion의 styled를 사용하는 경우</strong></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://velog.velcdn.com/images/corinthionia/post/0379b45d-cd71-4da3-a798-956575a20abd/image.png\" alt=\"styled를 사용하는 경우\"></p>\n<p><strong>그냥 &#x3C;StaticImage />를 사용하는 경우</strong></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://velog.velcdn.com/images/corinthionia/post/2e83630c-ccad-4cba-88ac-87a74900a5f9/image.png\" alt=\"그냥 StaticImage를 사용하는 경우\"></p>\n<br/>\n<h2>Gatsby 공식문서</h2>\n<p>아무리 봐도 고작 <code class=\"language-text\">styled</code> 사용 유무만 달라서 검색해 보다가 Gatsby 공식 문서의 내용을 보게 되었는데…</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>If you use Emotion you can use the provided css prop instead</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>Emotion을 사용하면 <code class=\"language-text\">css</code> prop을 사용해라!</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Unfortunately the css prop from styled-components turns the code into a styled function under the hood and as explained above StaticImage doesn’t support that syntax.\nYou can also use a regular style or className prop. Note that in all of these cases the styling is applied to the wrapper, not the image itself.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">StaticImage</code> 는 styled-components를 지원하지 않기 때문에 regular style이나 className prop을 이용해야 한다.</p>\n<h2>해결!</h2>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">css</code> prop을 이용하여 해결했다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> css <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">'@emotion/react'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> StaticImage <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">'gatsby-plugin-image'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>StaticImage\n  src<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"./cat.jpg\"</span>\n  alt<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"A kitten\"</span>\n  css<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>css<span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token string\">\n    width: 100%;\n    height: 205px;\n    object-fit: cover;\n  </span><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">/</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<h1>2. &#x3C;GatsbyImage/>에 스타일 적용하기</h1>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">&lt;GatsbyImage/></code>를 사용하여 프로필 사진을 띄웠는데, PC 화면에서 보면 스타일(border-radius)이 잘 적용돼서 나오지만, 모바일 화면에서는 적용되지 않았다!\n<img src=\"https://velog.velcdn.com/images/corinthionia/post/19566c3d-8442-4d96-a561-90690a1b4bdc/image.jpeg\" alt=\"\">\n그래서 찾아보니… <code class=\"language-text\">imgStyle</code>의 props로 넘겨 주면 된다고 한다.\n그래서 다음과같이 해결했다!</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>ProfileImage\n  image<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>profileImage<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n  alt<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"Profile image\"</span>\n  imgStyle<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token literal-property property\">borderRadius</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'40%'</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">/</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span></code></pre></div>\n<hr>\n<h3>참고</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.gatsbyjs.com/docs/reference/built-in-components/gatsby-plugin-image/#using-staticimage-with-css-in-js-libraries\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Gatsby 공식문서 - Gatsby Image plugin</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://stackoverflow.com/questions/66835241/gatsby-image-plugin-not-displaying-properly-on-ios-devices\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Gatsby-Image-Plugin not displaying properly on iOS devices</a></li>\n</ul>","frontmatter":{"title":"Gatsby의 StaticImage / GatsbyImage 스타일 적용하기","summary":"포스트 목록에 썸네일 이미지를 추가하고 싶어서 gatsby-plugin-image 라이브러리의 StaticImage로 대충 디자인 해 보고 있었다.그런데 emotion의 `styled`를 적용하면 이미지가 아예 뜨질 않았다 😳","date":"November 24, 2022","categories":["post","gatsby"]}}}]},"file":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","placeholder":{"fallback":"data:image/jpeg;base64,"},"images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/0a26d336dc62306ceb50b7ed12e4aefc/bbf83/profile-image.jpg","srcSet":"/static/0a26d336dc62306ceb50b7ed12e4aefc/a8e5a/profile-image.jpg 30w,\n/static/0a26d336dc62306ceb50b7ed12e4aefc/bea51/profile-image.jpg 60w,\n/static/0a26d336dc62306ceb50b7ed12e4aefc/bbf83/profile-image.jpg 120w,\n/static/0a26d336dc62306ceb50b7ed12e4aefc/7793c/profile-image.jpg 240w","sizes":"(min-width: 120px) 120px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/0a26d336dc62306ceb50b7ed12e4aefc/2b147/profile-image.webp 30w,\n/static/0a26d336dc62306ceb50b7ed12e4aefc/caa3b/profile-image.webp 60w,\n/static/0a26d336dc62306ceb50b7ed12e4aefc/b15f9/profile-image.webp 120w,\n/static/0a26d336dc62306ceb50b7ed12e4aefc/b5014/profile-image.webp 240w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"(min-width: 120px) 120px, 100vw"}]},"width":120,"height":120}},"publicURL":"/static/0a26d336dc62306ceb50b7ed12e4aefc/profile-image.jpg"}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/post/gatsby/gatsby-static-image/"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3575694552"],"slicesMap":{}}